<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-cyber-security-centre> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The NCSC acts as a bridge between industry and government, providing a unified source of advice, guidance and support on cyber security, including the management of cyber security incidents. NCSC is part of the Government Communications Headquarters ."@en .
